== Partial sets ==
In addition to the full sets above, there are some additional types of furniture items that only exist for some sets.
*'''Banners''': Consists of the {{item|Eye of the Accursed Banner}} and the {{item|Occult Legionnaire Banner}}. Crafted from [[Occult Brick]]s and [[Silk]].
*'''Monoliths''': Consists of the {{item|Astral Projector}}, crafted from [[Astral Monolith]]; the {{item|Exo Obelisk}}, crafted from [[Exo Plating]]; and the {{item|Monolith of the Accursed}}, crafted from Occult Bricks.
*'''Ritual Candles''': Consists of the {{item|Large Ritual Candle}} and the {{item|Ritual Candle}}. Crafted from Occult Bricks and [[Torches]].
*'''Sconces''': Consists of the {{item|Cosmilite Sconce}}, crafted from [[Cosmilite Brick]]s and Torches.


